{"tid":1829666,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「愛」 其實係一個百分數","createTime":"2020-01-19T03:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T03:27:27.000Z","uid":107157,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"99d7c1e952b464a7042904970a3aecd53919386d","tid":1829666,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T03:15:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">愛情 其實係 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">百分數</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當你愛上一個人，<br />\n你對佢既愛會係<span style=\"color: orange;\">100%</span>既愛<br />\n<br />\n當你愛上兩個人，<br />\n你對任何一方既愛都唔會係<span style=\"color: orange;\">100%</span><br />\n<br />\n當你愛A <span style=\"color: orange;\">50%</span>，<br />\n對B既愛就唔會超過<span style=\"color: orange;\">50%<br />\n</span><span style=\"color: red;\">愛越多人，愛既質量就會下降</span><br />\n-------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">受愛</span></span> 其實都係百分數<br />\n<br />\n當你受盡萬千寵愛既時候，<br />\n人地對你付出<span style=\"color: orange;\">100%</span>既愛<br />\n係你生命中只會可能係<span style=\"color: orange;\">1%</span><br />\n你根本唔會識得去珍惜<br />\n<br />\n而當有一日所有人離你而去既時候，<br />\n突然有人送上佢<span style=\"color: orange;\">1%</span>既愛，<br />\n但係你生命中就係<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">100%</span></span>既愛<br />\n你會失去理智咁守護住呢<span style=\"color: orange;\">1%</span>既愛<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">施比受更為有福</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nPlayer 都只不過係一種自我保護，<br />\n一個明智既投資者<br />\n<br />\n</div><br />\n參考例子:<br />\n1. 毒撚輕易愛上人<br />\n2. 收兵論<br />\n3. 共患難容易，共富貴難<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 自己既寵物走左，有感而發。"},{"pid":"e0225ab09e7eefbbea85abc4c5f854f89f185bba","tid":1829666,"uid":115234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T03:17:51.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"9fca8e64b9149973227789470ecf1f1addf389cd","tid":1829666,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T03:18: